216 void MainWindow::detect3D(int partAIndex, int partBIndex){
217  //detect objects here
218  pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGB>::Ptr detected(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGB>);
219  icpResult objectDetectionResult = filters->object_detection(currentCloud,models.at(partAIndex)->getModels(),models.at(partBIndex)->getModels());
220  displayNewPointCloud(filters->visualize_rgb(objectDetectionResult.cloud));

226  partBInTag = world * worldToTag * tagToCamera * objectDetectionResult.partBFinal;
227 
228  viewer1->addCoordinateSystem(0.2,frameA);
229  viewer1->addCoordinateSystem(0.2,frameB);
230 
231  QString partA = "X: ";

233  partA.append(", Y: ");

236  partA.append(QString::number(partAInTag(2,3)));
237 
238  QString partB = "X: ";

240  partB.append(", Y: ");
241  partB.append(QString::number(partBInTag(1,3)));
242  partB.append(", Z: ");
243  partB.append(QString::number(partBInTag(2,3)));
244 
245  printToLog("Position of part a in world:");

254 void MainWindow::detectAngle2D(double &part){
255  int counter = qnode.getCounter();
256  std::vector<double> temp;
257  temp.push_back(qnode.getTheta());
258  while(true){
259  while(qnode.getCounter() == counter);
260  counter = qnode.getCounter();
261  temp.push_back(qnode.getTheta());
262  if(temp.size() > 20){
263  double d = 0.0;
264  for(int i=0; i<temp.size(); i++) {
265  d = d + temp.at(i);
266  }
267  double average = d/(double)temp.size();
268  part = average;
269  return;
270  }
271  }
272 }

515 void MainWindow::on_auto2dSecondPartButton_clicked(bool check){
516  if(!movedToPartB) {
517  Q_EMIT move_ag1(homeX,homeY1,homeZ,homeRoll,homePitch*(M_PI/180.0),homeYaw);
518  Q_EMIT move_ag2(partAInTag(0,3),partAInTag(1,3),1.45,0,3.1415,(-23.5)*(M_PI/180.0));
519  Q_EMIT move_ag2(partBInTag(0,3),partBInTag(1,3),1.45,0,3.1415,(-23.5)*(M_PI/180.0));
520  Q_EMIT move_ag2(partBInTag(0,3),partBInTag(1,3),1.39,0,3.1415,(-23.5)*(M_PI/180.0));
521  Q_EMIT setProcessImageKeypointDescriptor("SIFT", "SIFT");
522  Q_EMIT setProcessImageMatchingPicture(partBpath);
523  Q_EMIT setProcessImageDepthLambda(0.153);
524  movedToPartB = true;
525  } else {
526  double correctionY = partBInTag(0,3)-qnode.getYoffset();
527  double correctionX = partBInTag(1,3)-qnode.getXoffset();
528  Q_EMIT move_ag2(correctionY,correctionX,1.39,0,3.1415,(-23.5)*(M_PI/180.0));
529  partBInTag(0,3) = correctionY;
530  partBInTag(1,3) = correctionX;
531  }
532 }

646 void MainWindow::on_create_training_set_button_clicked(bool check){
647  QString msg = "";
648  QString partName;
649  QString filePath = QFileDialog::getOpenFileName(this, tr("Open STL File"),"/home/minions",tr("STL cad model (*.stl)"));
650  if(!filePath.isEmpty()){
651  bool ok;
652  partName = QInputDialog::getText(this, tr("Name the part"), tr("Part name"), QLineEdit::Normal, tr(""), &ok);
653  if(!partName.isEmpty() && ok){
654  }
655  else{
656  return;
657  }
658  }
659  else{
660  return;
661  }
662  msg.append("Rendering file: ");
663  msg.append(filePath);
664  msg.append(", as partname: ");
665  msg.append(partName);
666  printToLog(msg);
667  pcl::PolygonMesh mesh;
668  pcl::io::loadPolygonFileSTL(filePath.toStdString(),mesh);
669 
670  pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZ> scaled_mesh;
671  Eigen::Matrix4f scaleMatrix = Eigen::Matrix4f::Identity();
672  scaleMatrix(0,0)=0.001f;
673  scaleMatrix(1,1)=0.001f;
674  scaleMatrix(2,2)=0.001f;
675 
676  pcl::fromPCLPointCloud2(mesh.cloud,scaled_mesh);
677  pcl::transformPointCloud(scaled_mesh,scaled_mesh,scaleMatrix);
678  pcl::toPCLPointCloud2(scaled_mesh, mesh.cloud);
679 
680  ModelLoader *render = new ModelLoader(mesh, partName.toStdString());
681  render->setCloudResolution(ui.resolution_combobox->currentText().toInt());
682  render->setTesselation_level(ui.tesselation_level_combobox->currentIndex()+1);
683  render->populateLoader();
684 }

698 void MainWindow::on_loadPCDButton_clicked(bool check){
699  runStream = false;
700  QString fileName = QFileDialog::getOpenFileName(this, tr("Open File"),"/home/minions",tr("PointCloud (*.pcd)"));
701  if(fileName.length() != 0){
702  QString tmpstring = "Loading .pcd from ";
703  tmpstring.append(fileName);
704  printToLog(tmpstring);
705  if(ui.loadRgbCheckbox->isChecked()){
706  pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGB>::Ptr displayCloud(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZRGB>);
707  if(pcl::io::loadPCDFile<pcl::PointXYZRGB>(fileName.toUtf8().constData(), *displayCloud) == -1)
708  {
709  return;
710  }
711 
712  displayNewPointCloud(filters->visualize_rgb(displayCloud));
713  }
714  else{
715  pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZ>::Ptr displayCloud(new pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZ>);
716  if(pcl::io::loadPCDFile<pcl::PointXYZ>(fileName.toUtf8().constData(), *displayCloud) == -1)
717  {
718  return;
719  }
720  *currentCloud = *displayCloud;
721  displayNewPointCloud(filters->visualize(displayCloud));
722  }
723  }
724 }
